examples.answer:
The VirtualBox configuration explicitly sets up port forwarding for Janus on ports **8088**, **8089**, and **8188**. These are specified in the port-opening scripts in `README.md` (lines 48–50):

```bash
VBoxManage modifyvm "laGGer" --natpf1 "janus1,tcp,,8088,,8088";
VBoxManage modifyvm "laGGer" --natpf1 "janus1,tcp,,8089,,8089";
VBoxManage modifyvm "laGGer" --natpf1 "janus1,tcp,,8188,,8188";
```

